layout.house_prompt: A tiny house with a bedroom, a living-kitchen, and a bathroom. The bedroom has a bed and a wooden dresser. The living-kitchen has a sofa, a dining table with two chairs, and a refrigerator. The bathroom has a toilet and a sink.

living_room.text_description: A modern minimalist tiny-house living-kitchen combined space with a sofa; a small dining table with two chairs; and an intentional kitchenette zone with a refrigerator and a compact work run planned along the shared plumbing wall with the bathroom (sink/services aligned), with cooking ventilation routed to an exterior wall for exhaust and realistic work-zone clearances.

bedroom.text_description: A modern minimalist tiny-house bedroom with a bed and a wooden dresser.

hallway.text_description: A modern minimalist tiny-house entry vestibule/micro-buffer that improves privacy between the main living area and the bathroom (no additional furniture).

bathroom.text_description: A modern minimalist tiny-house bathroom with a toilet and a sink.
